The '''Soft Heart Cantina''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located in [[Grid 19]] of the [[Southern Underground/Legends|Southern Underground]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Imperial Center]]. In the year [[2 BBY/Legends|2 BBY]], it burned down along with an entire city block, in a fire officially attributed to arson. While fire suppressors were supposed to protect the uninsured cantina, these mysteriously failed. The owner, [[Memah Roothes]], and her bouncer, [[Rodo]], agreed to transfer to [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|another location]] owned by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to work a new military cantina. Roothes named the cantina the [[Hard Heart Cantina/Legends|Hard Heart Cantina]], after her original cantina. The cantina was known to have [[Membrosia/Legends|membrosia]].<ref name="Death Star (novel)">[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref>

